## Early life

Kohli was born on 5 November 1988 in Delhi, India. He is the son of Prem Kohli, a former cricketer who played for Delhi in the 1980s. His father was a fast bowler and his mother, Saroj Kohli, was a national level hockey player. He has a younger brother, Vikas, who is also a cricketer. Kohli's father died of a heart attack in 2006.
